data.description: Come build your dream custom home in the Texas Hill Country in River Chase which offers some of the best amenities in the area. River Chase has a gorgeous Guadalupe River park where you can enjoy sitting in the clear cool blue water. In addition, the community provides a pool, a kiddy pool, tennis counts and a gym. With the larger parcel of property (3 plus acres), privacy is at its best, Your home can be nestled around the mature oak trees - make it a private estate. Many flat building sites on the property - property will be an easy build. River Chase is 15 minutes to Gruene, entertainment, shopping and restaurants with an easy drive on four lane FM 306 - escape the hassle of the city living. Come, live and enjoy the good life in the Texas Hill Country.
